{"tid":1803754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完民陣既記者會，我誠懇地請求手足唔好去1月1嗰送頭集會","createTime":"2019-12-30T12:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T07:32:18.000Z","uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee776d5958249add71792b1b724caaa4221e21a","tid":1803754,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"睇多幾次就會明咩事架啦"},{"pid":"adc23ef106f7f4ffaab57cd9e2c5cc1f44debc69","tid":1803754,"uid":198590,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 山齊士超級綠洲</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>12月1遊行有200萬人,我派Lm既連登仔,每人2000蚊,絕不走數 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>投完票贏完啦<br />\n仲唔出嚟</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1761734/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1761734/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑製造派錢假象 <blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/dA8N0Lx.png\" /></blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>不如幫幫白鴿黨裝修 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>11年同15年屌人民力量同熱血公民票<br />\n今日就鳩沙田友既票<br />\n咁就送左席比民賤聯<br />\n道歉Sorry好撚假囉<br />\n人地議席就無左咩都無<br />\n你地今次就大勝食咁多議席<br />\n仲要好多區比你地逼到退選讓路含淚投<br />\n<br />\n既然你地食人血饅頭食得咁開心<br />\n手足陣間不如發夢去是旦一個白鴿黨既辦事署裝下修<br />\n反正你地今次賺咁多經費咁多人工<br />\n比2條路你地揀<br />\n裝修/捐一半人工做抗爭基金<br />\n就係咁</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>新口號同洗腦金句！想贏既入嚟同我宣傳出去 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>將香港人 反抗<br />\n變做<br />\n香港人 返工<br />\n成個口號幾撚震撼</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>保護休班警,你我有責 - #4</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔好搞休班警<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實借運動識女溝女有咩問題 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>CCtai班友仔做咩咁敏感<br />\n大家都係有相同興趣同諗法<br />\n傾得埋再交換contact上埋床有咩問題<br />\nCCTai班小朋友真係大驚小怪</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/965Ev7E.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"ba56aa17a0d4aaff1f68615c59c4b02e22d444f2","tid":1803754,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"夠鐘收錢"},{"pid":"fa0c1d24a7f5beeb0bb6134c25afa25f0e365ccc","tid":1803754,"uid":48432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"屌你講啲唔講啲 淨係喺度吹風"},{"pid":"1b1a54522280382811b1ac7d4753a96350046095","tid":1803754,"uid":60916,"like"